{"tid":322141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪忘記咗臨立會？","createTime":"2017-07-14T15:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T01:50:17.000Z","uid":78732,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7b3d851ccaee35c131a0921b0f37c7385ed0e07","tid":322141,"uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"當年全個臨立會都係建制派，做咗啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong>修改選舉制度</strong>：由單議席單票制改為比例代表制，及引入最大餘額法<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>通過《立法會條例》</strong>：任何議員議案，不得北京首肯，必然在分組點票之下被否決<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>公安條例重臨</strong>：將遊行集會通知制度更改為「不反對通知書」制度，並於1997年6月14日，一日內三讀通過。<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>廢除工會集體談判權</strong><br />\n<br />\n仲集體總辭？"},{"pid":"5480971705d62c4b51d951e5489ca8697d76d51c","tid":322141,"uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"傻的嗎？"},{"pid":"dd19adc09f08763bca2ce0651ef2efb775ccc05d","tid":322141,"uid":78732,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"如果我係梁美芬，你哋泛民總辭，我即刻推《辱警罪》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1ee4c8afd353c3ece02e1be21438b74e795c89","tid":322141,"uid":7716,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"唔總辭<br />\n2018 23條part 1<br />\n2019 23條part 2<br />\n2020 23條正式落實<br />\n斬件上無人當一回事<br />\n橫掂所以民主派都唔會再阻到任何法案"},{"pid":"257e1ca5217335d2f9e52ff0fea07afc5302d003","tid":322141,"uid":993,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"所以宜家班泛民阻止到政改？一地兩檢？議事規則修改？"},{"pid":"3d5ba62b6ff8c4338282afc2884de453272c9d78","tid":322141,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:12:56.000Z","msg":"明嘅<br />\n細路仔唔知揾食艱難啫"},{"pid":"3c5f578fc69ea675ff176faf0d67f3b7c8938534","tid":322141,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年全個臨立會都係建制派，做咗啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong>修改選舉制度</strong>：由單議席單票制改為比例代表制，及引入最大餘額法<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>通過《立法會條例》</strong>：任何議員議案，不得北京首肯，必然在分組點票之下被否決<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>公安條例重臨</strong>：將遊行集會通知制度更改為「不反對通知書」制度，並於1997年6月14日，一日內三讀通過。<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>廢除工會集體談判權</strong><br />\n<br />\n仲集體總辭？</blockquote><br />\n分組點票係基本法附件二規定，唔係立法會條例。"},{"pid":"e040e9c480bbb9fc9b5bbb59aec279deac0c709d","tid":322141,"uid":24140,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果我係梁美芬，你哋泛民總辭，我即刻推《辱警罪》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家泛民阻到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3664a09ea5c2a05600960d227c64e87709eaad","tid":322141,"uid":52265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果我係梁美芬，你哋泛民總辭，我即刻推《辱警罪》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家泛民阻到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直選已經係16比14泛民"},{"pid":"355e22e769dd8ae5b244defb5d3f430161eeaf49","tid":322141,"uid":46640,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"你唔辭都冇足夠議席阻止上述事情發生，柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b807a195e600884c4de2c125a19c24b87c06d510","tid":322141,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:27:16.000Z","msg":"On9仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bee8f62c6268d81f0e0485fa97cc54a2887cb9","tid":322141,"uid":89514,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:01:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cf85779f66cb8eb1abbc5a6106344378afbe5d6","tid":322141,"uid":17682,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":